imilar technologies that they use. In addition, because we have no control over such third-party sites and resources, you acknowledge and agree that Bushland Bliss is not responsible for the availability of such third-party sites or resources, and that Bushland Bliss does not endorse or is responsible or liable for any content, advertising, products, or other materials on or available from such third-party sites or resources.</span></p>
